<html lang='en'>
	<head>
		<meta charset='UTF-8' />
		<meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
		<link rel='stylesheet' href='welcome.css' />
		<title>Welcome to the Team!</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class='container'>
			<h2>Welcome Aboard, {{name}}!</h2>
			<p>We're thrilled to have you on board. If you have any questions, feel free to contact us at
				{{support_email}}.</p>
			<h3>Onboarding Checklist</h3>
			<ul class='checklist'>
				<li>Set up your company email account</li>
				<li>Complete your profile on our internal platform</li>
				<li>Schedule your first team meeting</li>
				<li>Read through the employee handbook</li>
			</ul>
			<h3>Interesting Facts</h3>
			<p>Did you know? Our company was founded in the year
				{{foundation_year}}
				and has been on an incredible journey ever since!</p>
			<p>Another fact: We have employees from over {{number_of_countries}} different countries!</p>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>